Package org.jboss.windup.config.loader

Interface LabelProviderLoader

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    XMLLabelProviderLoader
    public interface LabelProviderLoader
    Defines a way Windup can load LabelProviders. We might have multiple ways of loading a LabelProviders for instance might have XMLLabelProviderLoader, JSONLabelproviderLoader, JavaLabelProviderLoader, etc.

    Carlos Feria
